@globe Thank you, great work!
For people with game starting issues, you have to wait some time for game to start, don't run launcher multiple times. If you have firewall and game won't start (you see only black screen), you must ALT+TAB or CTRL+ALT+DEL to change to firewall and set permission. Update DX, GPU driver, install Games for Windows - LIVE
